title: Jesse Parete
text: Jesse Parete (born 20 April 1993) is a <a href="New%20Zealand">New Zealand</a> <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player for the <a href="Highlanders%20%28rugby%20union%29">Highlanders</a> in <a href="Super%20Rugby">Super Rugby</a>. His position is in the back row. He made his Super Rugby debut vs the <a href="Jaguares%20%28Super%20Rugby%29">Jaguares</a> in Round 12, scoring a try in the final minutes of the match.
